&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;The Benefits and Leave Partner is a hands-on administrator responsible for delivering a seamless benefits and leave experience for Alarm.com employees. In this role, you&#39;ll own the full lifecycle of our benefits programs — medical, dental, vision, 401(k), FSA/HSA, COBRA, and more — while managing leave of absence cases from intake through return-to-work. You&#39;ll serve as the primary point of contact for employees and HR partners navigating benefits questions, qualifying life events, and accommodation requests, and you&#39;ll work cross-functionally with Finance, Legal, and third-party vendors to keep our programs running accurately and compliantly. This role is a strong fit for someone who thrives in the details, takes ownership of their work, and genuinely enjoys helping people navigate complex benefit situations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
