&lt;li&gt;Own benefit enrollments, qualifying life events, and employee data changes within HR systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to employee inquiries regarding benefits eligibility, coverage, and claims, providing an exceptional level of customer service to our internal and external partners (HRBPs, employees, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive leave of absence programs including FMLA, STD/LTD, military leave, and applicable state leave programs; manage cases from intake through return-to-work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own accommodation processes, including ADA requests, in partnership with HR and Legal as appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Invoice &amp;amp; Billing Administration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
