&lt;li&gt;Resolve discrepancies with vendors, hiring managers, and Finance to ensure billing accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner cross-functionally with Accounts Payable to ensure timely processing and payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance &amp;amp; Data Integrity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
