&lt;li&gt;Work with Software Engineers to design and implement features that interact with the cloud.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Product Managers and quality engineers to ensure the products meet &lt;a href=&quot;http://alarm.com/&quot; data-ext-link-init=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Alarm.com&lt;/a&gt;&#39;s standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively and collaborate with others to ensure the timely delivery of projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
