&lt;li&gt;Design, develop, and manage detailed project plans in a fast-paced, dynamic environment with multiple parallel workstreams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead key stakeholders in defining project scope and gathering accurate, complete business and technical requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and manage cost estimates, milestones, dependencies, and resource requirements to ensure successful project delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate cross-functional teams to execute on technical requirements, enhancements, and bug fixes aligned with service launch timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate closely with cross-functional teams - including field ops, legal, sales operations, certifications, localization, training, account management, technical account management, support, and marketing - to plan and execute global product deployments across international markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify, communicate, and mitigate risks to ensure projects are delivered on time and with high quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure projects are thoroughly documented to support transparency, continuity, and risk mitigation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong relationships with internal teams, partners, and stakeholders to ensure delivery against commitments.&lt;/li&gt;
